nodes.text: Dweezel was a gooey pastry common to the city of Mos Espa on the planet Tatooine. They were invented by the culinary genius Professor Umlaut. Ingredients of dweezel consisted of dough, a berry filling, a starchy filling of tubers, and a fruit glaze. An ice cream man on Endor was known to have a plate of dweezel in his possession.
